FBIS3-41357 "jptdd008__l94065" JPRS-TDD-94-008-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 23 February 1994 NEAR EAST & SOUTH ASIA INDIA Mandrax Destined for Mozambique Seized at Bombay Dock 94WD0201B Madras THE HINDU in English 29 Dec 93 p 4 94WD0201B Madras THE HINDU Language: English Article Type:CSO [Article: "Narcotics Seizure"] [Text] Bombay, Dec. 28. The Narcotics Control Bureau (NCB) of Bombay Customs seized 2210 packets of mandrax tablets weighing 1435 kg and valued at Rs. 30 crore in the international market from a export consignment at Indira dock in South Bombay this afternoon. According to NCB sources, the consignment which was marked water heaters was to be shipped to Mozambique. Two persons have been detained in this connection.
